definitions.definition: a person (of either sex) entering the first year of an institution, especially a high school ( ninth grade for US , grade 9 for Canada , grade 7 for Philippines ), a university , or legislative body
examples: At the time I was a wide-eyed freshman , but I was soon to grow jaded and cynical.

definitions.definition: a novice ; one in the rudiments of knowledge
